ABOUT THE PREVIEW VERSION

This is the preview version of NSX. It only includes 5 levels to make you see
what will the game look like..... We have 55 levels in 11 worlds, with
different gfx and anims.... But the main idea is all the same.........

This game is tested on several A500 and A1200 configurations,
it worked ok, we didn't try it on A600s and A4000's but i think it works...
By the way the use of this program is at your own risk...We removed the
'hi-sc save' routines to guaratie and we also think that it's pretty harmless
but be carefull and use LEFT mouse button in the game to exit this preview..

Final version will be released very soon.... with a little shareware fee...
(I don't think but maybe)... The release date is not certain yet but it will
be released as soon as that some little bugs are removed..

Do send your mails/messages/bug reports/WhatEverYouWant to:

